  <h1>Nodezator - A generalist python node editor</h1>

  <h2>Introduction</h2>

  <p>Nodezator is a generalist Python node editor. It allows you to connect Python functions (and callables in general) visually in order to produce flexible parametric behaviour/data/applications/snippets.</p>

  <p>For tutorials/examples/roadmap and more go to <a href="https://nodezator.com">nodezator.com</a>.</p>

